        <br />
        <p>Obtain ETSC wallet address at <a href="https://wallet.ethereumsocial.kr/" target="_blank">https://wallet.ethereumsocial.kr/</a></p>
        <p>Download <a href="https://github.com/ethereum-mining/ethminer/releases" target="blank">ethminer</a> for you operation system</p>
        <h4><img src="windows.svg" height="20"> Windows</h4>
        <p> Create <code>miner.bat</code> file with following content and run it.</p>
        <pre><code>
setx GPU_FORCE_64BIT_PTR 0
setx GPU_MAX_HEAP_SIZE 100
setx GPU_USE_SYNC_OBJECTS 1
setx GPU_MAX_ALLOC_PERCENT 100
setx GPU_SINGLE_ALLOC_PERCENT 100
<kbd>&lt;path to miner&gt;</kbd>/ethminer.exe -F {{config.HttpHost}}:8888/<kbd>&lt;wallet&gt;</kbd>/<kbd>&lt;worker&gt;</kbd> -G --farm-recheck 200
        </code></pre>
        <p>
          <code>&lt;wallet&gt;</code> is your ETSC wallet address, example:
          <code>0xd34699FD152fe38CAacD3C096F6abb1cd79e88b2</code>.
          <br>
          <code>&lt;worker&gt;</code> is custom name for worker, example : <code>rig01</code>, <code>rig02</code>
        </p>
      </div>
      <br />
      <div class="paper border-top-0">
        <h4><img src="linux.svg" height="20"> Linux</h4>
        <p>Create <code>miner.sh</code> file with following content:</p>
        <pre><code>
#!/bin/bash
export GPU_FORCE_64BIT_PTR=0
export GPU_MAX_HEAP_SIZE=100
export GPU_USE_SYNC_OBJECTS=1
export GPU_MAX_ALLOC_PERCENT=100
export GPU_SINGLE_ALLOC_PERCENT=100
<kbd>&lt;path to miner&gt;</kbd>/ethminer -F {{config.HttpHost}}:8888/<kbd>&lt;wallet&gt;</kbd>/<kbd>&lt;worker&gt;</kbd> -G --farm-recheck 200
        </code></pre>
        <p>Make it executable: <code>chmod +x &lt;path to .sh file&gt;</code> and run it</p>
        <p>
          <code>&lt;wallet&gt;</code> is your ETSC wallet address, example:
          <code>0xd34699FD152fe38CAacD3C096F6abb1cd79e88b2</code>.
          <br>
          <code>&lt;worker&gt;</code> is custom name for worker, example : <code>rig01</code>, <code>rig02</code>
        </p>
